I just created a new calendar for my team, in addition to have the ability to create custom event types like – Launches, Webinars, Conferences etc (which I could easily do if you let me simply rename an event event type  – I'd like to be able to create a new set of events based on an ical file.

For example, I want to have an event type in my team's calendar that shows all US public holidays which I can easily import from here:

http://www.calendarlabs.com/ical-calendar-holidays.php

