On https://extranet.atlassian.com/display/GHDEV/JIRA+Agile+T+Shirt+RSVP there's an event macro. Trying to fill out its form and clicking on the labels for the shirt size checkboxes focuses on the colour text input.

This is because the colour input and all the checkboxes have received the HTML id "$column-10937" instead of the correct field name (e.g. the email field has "email-10937"). Looks like a velocity parameter that wasn't replaced.

